Actions.ActionName: ~~~ CREATE GROUP ACTION CLIPBOARD IF NEEDED ~~~
IF NAMED CLIPBOARD DOES NOT EXIST, PROMT USER

ThenActions.Title: KM Group Action Clipboard is EMPTY
ThenActions.Text:
DO NOT STOP MACRO

Follow these instructions:
(1) Select a KM Group Action that you would like to use
(2) Press CONTINUE button on this dialog

ThenActions.Title: Group Action has been SAVED to the Named Clipboard
ThenActions.Text:
Now, 

1. Select the KM Actions you want to put into this Group Action
2. PRESS CONTINUE Button on this dialog
